+        # ---------------------------------------------------------------
+        # Crawl Verify Gateway cutover (one-verify-server consolidation).
+        # When a country is in crawl_verify_allowlist AND the API key is
+        # set, route to crawl-verify instead of the legacy per-country
+        # adapter. Allowlist is a comma-separated env var
+        # (CRAWL_VERIFY_ALLOWLIST) so flipping a country in/out is a
